			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>So this Sunday I had nothing better to do so I decided to head over to the Monte Casino Bird Gardens to go visit our feathery friends of nature. I did not walk among the whole park but managed to catch a glimpse of the different enclosures with the variety of different animals the have, their motto all implies this: &#8220;Inspired to Conserve&#8221;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>I went to<a href="http://www.montecasino.co.za/entertainment/family/Bird%20Gardens/Pages/flight_of_fantasy.aspx"> Flight of Fantasy</a> show which takes place in their Tuscan Amphitheater which shows their colourful and talented show birds with breathtaking displays of unrestrained flight. Be sure to visit the show and have an educational experience of these birds and their behaviors, you won&#8217;t be disappointed !!</p>
